{"tid":702272,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"知你唔會諗起我","createTime":"2018-06-14T18:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T00:17:05.000Z","uid":178658,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7404c61bd240b9ff61197627cf80a762781b7549","tid":702272,"uid":178658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T18:01:37.000Z","msg":"但你仍然不停出現係我腦海中，知你宜家幸福過同我起埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n好撚辛苦，明明三個月啦已經，點解個心仲會痛，仲會周不時諗起你，心情係有啲唔甘心，有啲唔開心，有啲唔捨得，仲有殘餘嘅個小小愛<br />\n<br />\n每日笑完開心完，情緒平伏完之後就好撚痛，有咩方法自救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44169737541017b7f698f99dbdbac2edbf7ea44","tid":702272,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T18:03:38.000Z","msg":"冇，唯有唔去諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936b89df681c996abf9308f81922f137f5603a20","tid":702272,"uid":170616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T18:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我希望用一個星期放低佢"},{"pid":"d7e9caf3e958d3c859e7fdd564ccfd9d87bc5dd0","tid":702272,"uid":169468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T18:11:06.000Z","msg":"好撚明白呢種感覺，但要頂住呀，要笑住過每一日，要過得比佢好，搵多啲嘢做，要比自己知道自己唔係為咗佢而生存，冇咗佢自己嘅生活都可以多姿多彩"},{"pid":"757daa2f3ea91c3096963bc35b8ab965a7d88659","tid":702272,"uid":94094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T18:54:44.000Z","msg":"完全明白體會到你心情<br />\n明知作已經唔會返轉頭<br />\n但都唔知點建好掛住佢一齊既時光<br />\n周不時會發夢見到<br />\n諗起分手個刻個心仲拿住拿住<br />\n唔識放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39888d8ecad4fb0c30979e5f846155cdfb5ce04","tid":702272,"uid":69473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T18:58:45.000Z","msg":"能抽空想我也就當是我生命大成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好希望妳會有諗起我，會有掛住我嘅一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aab3a1c213f1b3d18fdf6b20b09a88c23b5b04b","tid":702272,"uid":182134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T23:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係就黎三個月<br />\n好返一陣又沉返落去<br />\n好掛住佢<br />\n明知佢無可能返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010d6fdde9f167b3e6d9d30ff96f30fb9d697a6d","tid":702272,"uid":181326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:25:40.000Z","msg":"做d正經事，充實自己，你會變得更可愛"},{"pid":"034e7109e30a679d0b15e8d6ed8229e5631568f9","tid":702272,"uid":120418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:30:05.000Z","msg":"時間會沖淡一切"},{"pid":"09874aa09998ba08c4983b23c1544a1dad8bacde","tid":702272,"uid":93471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T19:25:24.000Z","msg":"加油 我幾年都沖唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6fe03777eaf2023fa0e7d6f7633c682da6f1d8","tid":702272,"uid":181326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T00:17:05.000Z","msg":"無咁快，當愛變成往事"}]}